Full builds and features
    DupontTeijinfilms (link to jobs portal)

    Who is DupontTeijinfilms?
    Dupont Teijin films is a mylar flims production company.
    They are the one of the biggest mylar films producers in the
    US.
    
    What was the problem?
    There previous website (wayback machine), was confusing and 
    difficult to navigate. The site istelf did not drive sales and
    DupontTeijinfilms was looking to improve that.

    What I delivered.
    I built a custom theme wordpress site. Based of a custom design
    and stratigy from inhouse designers. 
    I implemented a full custom theme, built
    with ACF, custom post types and a sass front end. This was my
    first full wordpress site, as I usually work on larger engineering
    projects.

